57.4	Tommy_Lee	Tommy Lee	Thomas Lee Bass (born October 3, 1962), best known as Tommy Lee, is an American musician and founding member of glam metal band Mötley Crüe. As well as being the band's long-term drummer, Lee founded rap-metal band Methods of Mayhem, and has pursued solo musical projects. He has been married to model Elaine Bergen and actresses Heather Locklear and Pamela Anderson.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Tommy_Lee_2012.jpg/220px-Tommy_Lee_2012.jpg
